#: ../../merchants/getting-started.rst:262
msgid ""
"Next, go to CoinPayments.net and `sign up "
"<https://www.coinpayments.net/register>`_ to create an account. Once you are"
" logged in, go to **Account -> Coin Acceptance Settings** and enable Dash, "
"as well as optionally entering a withdrawal address. Next, go to **Account "
"-> Account Settings** and copy **Your Merchant ID** from the **Basic "
"Settings** area into a text file. Then navigate to the **Merchant Settings**"
" section and enter a long, random series of characters for the **IPN "
"Secret**. Copy this code to your temporary file as well."
